text_bem: Then shall cease wars and savage times become mild, and Remus and Quirinus, brothers twain, with hooyan Faith and Vesta undefiled, shall give the law, with iron bolt and chain firmly closed the gates of Janus shall remain, Inside, the Fiend of Discord, raised on horrid arms, unbound in the fane, bound a hundred brass knots behind, and smiled with gory teeth must grind his grey.
text_en: "Then wars shall cease and savage times grow mild, / and Remus and Quirinus, brethren twain, / with hoary Faith and Vesta undefiled, / shall give the law. With iron bolt and chain / firm-closed the gates of Janus shall remain. / Within, the Fiend of Discord, high reclined / on horrid arms, unheeded in the fane, / bound with a hundred brazen knots behind, / and grim with gory jaws, his grisly teeth shall grind."
